OL,6,FA man suffered fatal injuries when he
OL,7,Fgot caught in a bin lorry's compaction
OL,8,Fequipment, a jury has heard.
OL,10,FDavid Carpenter, 60, died while
OL,11,Fcollecting bins on Guild Road in
OL,12,FCoventry on January 19 2023.
OL,14,FThe inquest into his death reopened on
OL,15,FTuesday where his family described him
OL,16,Fas a "lovable, warm and humble" man.
