OL,3,CBin collector died after he was lifted
OL,4,Cinto lorry's equipment
OL,6,FAfter the jury was sworn in at
OL,7,FCoventry's council buildings, coroner
OL,8,FDelroy Henry described how Mr
OL,9,FCarpenter was working as a team of
OL,10,Fthree collecting bins around the
OL,11,Fstreets of Coventry on the day he died.
OL,13,FHe said that Mr Carpenter had been a
OL,14,Frefuse collector since he was 18, with
OL,15,Fmore than 40 years of experience in
OL,16,Fthat line of work.
