OL,3,CBin collector died after he was lifted
OL,4,Cinto lorry's equipment
OL,6,FOn the morning he died, he was lifted
OL,7,Fby one of the rear lifting platforms
OL,8,Finto the automatic compaction
OL,9,Fequipment which caused his fatal
OL,10,Finjuries, the jury heard.
OL,12,FHis stepdaughter Claire Chetwynd spoke
OL,13,Fon behalf of the family saying he was
OL,14,Fa "loving father and stepfather" and
OL,15,Fthat his death has left a huge gap in
OL,16,Ftheir lives and hearts.
OL,18,FThe court was shown CCTV from the
OL,19,Fmorning Mr Carpenter died.
