OL,3,CBin collector died after he was lifted
OL,4,Cinto lorry's equipment
OL,6,FIt's from a camera pointing down at
OL,7,Fthe back of the bin lorry, with the
OL,8,Ftwo loading platforms that lift bins
OL,9,Finto the compactor in clear view.
OL,11,FIt shows approximately one minute of
OL,12,FMr Carpenter and the other collector
OL,13,Fbringing bins to the lorry as normal,
OL,14,Fthen he is shown loading a bin onto
OL,15,Fone of the platforms and reaching
OL,16,Facross to the other.
OL,18,FThe footage then shows Mr Carpenter
OL,19,Fbeing lifted and thrown into the
OL,20,Fmachinery in the back of the lorry,
OL,21,Fwhich only lasted a matter of seconds.
