OL,6,FThe coroner warned it might be
OL,7,Fupsetting footage to watch and
OL,8,Fproceedings were paused briefly
OL,9,Fafterwards for the family who were
OL,10,Fvisibly shaken by what they were shown.
OL,12,FThe bin lorry driver spoke in court
OL,13,Fand described the various safety
OL,14,Fchecks he would undertake before each
OL,15,Fshift, saying nothing was out of the
OL,16,Fordinary.
