OL,3,CBin collector died after he was lifted
OL,4,Cinto lorry's equipment
OL,6,FHe described how the lifting systems
OL,7,Fat the back of the lorry operate and
OL,8,Fhow sunlight was hitting the back
OL,9,Fcamera, making the view he had on the
OL,10,Fscreen in the cabin blurry which would
OL,11,Fshow the rear of the lorry.
OL,13,FHe recalled moving the lorry forward,
OL,14,Fthen hearing shouting as the other bin
OL,15,Fcollector hit the emergency button and
OL,16,Fran to the cabin to say Mr Carpenter
OL,17,Fhad been injured, but neither of them
OL,18,Fat that moment knew exactly what had
OL,19,Fhappened to him.
