OL,6,FIn a statement about Mr Carpenter's
OL,7,Fdeath, the Health and Safety Executive
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are continuing to
OL,9,Finvestigate this incident and will
OL,10,Fsupport the coroner throughout the
OL,11,Finquest.
OL,13,F"We continue to work with industry to
OL,14,Fensure that refuse collection vehicles
OL,15,Fmeet the required level of safety."
